room_title: Escape room "Saving Christmas" by Great Escape Mystery Rooms in Fort Smith
room_description: It's Christmas Eve and your parents sit you down to break the bad news: Mom hid all of the presents and now she can't remember where they are! She left herself some hints so this wouldn't happen (again), but needs your help finding them since it's almost Christmas morning. Follow the clues mom left to help save Christmas for your family!
